const QUESTIONS = [
"What does success actually mean to you right now — not the LinkedIn version?",
"When did you last feel genuinely out of your depth, and what did that teach you?",
"What belief are you holding that most people around you would disagree with?",
"If you stripped away the title tomorrow, who are you?",
"What's the decision you made that looked wrong to everyone else but you were certain about?",
"What's the gap between who you present to your board and who you actually are?",
"Where is the energy in your industry right now — and where is it dying?",
"What are you most afraid people will discover about how you're running this organisation?",
"What does the next generation of leaders in your sector fundamentally misunderstand?",
"If AI, quantum and automation reshape your sector completely in 10 years, what's your honest assessment of whether your organisation will survive?",
"What would you do differently if you had no obligation to the current stakeholders?",
"What's the conversation your board needs to have but nobody's willing to start?",
"When you look at the energy transition — are you leading it, managing it, or hoping it resolves itself?",
"What do you need to unlearn to lead effectively through the next decade?",
